(370, 'Cow & Gate 2 Follow On Baby Milk Formula 800g', NULL, 6, NULL, 2890, NULL, 0, '4AHWHZ', 'gm', 800, 'single', 50, '1655707308.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, '<p>When it comes to looking after your little one, support care and nutrition all help. Did you know that from 6 months old your baby needs more iron in their diet? Our follow-on milk can lend a helping hand to support your little one&rsquo;s nutritional needs as part of a varied, balanced diet, right up until they turn 1 year old.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Vitamin D &amp; Calcium for normal bone development.</li>\r\n<li>Iron to support normal cognitive development.</li>\r\n<li>Complement a weaning diet</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Ingredients: </strong></p>\r\n<p>Lactose (from Milk), Skimmed Milk, Vegetable Oils (Palm Oil, Rapeseed Oil, Coconut Oil, Sunflower Oil), Galacto-Oligosaccharides (GOS) (from Milk), Fructo-Oligossacharides (FOS), Calcium Carbonate, Potassium Chloride, Vitamin C, Choline Chloride, Taurine, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Iron Sulphate, L-Tryptophan, Inositol, Vitamin E, L-Isoleucine, Uridine 5&prime;-Monophosphate Sodium Salt, Zinc Sulphate, Cytidine 5&prime;-Monophoshate, L-Cysteine Hydrochloride, Adenosine 5&prime;-Monophoshapte, Inosine 5&prime;-Monophosphate Sodium Salt, Niacin, Guanosine 5&prime;-Monophosphate Sodium Salt, L-Carnitine, Pantothenic Acid, Folic Acid, Copper Sulphate, Vitamin A, Biotin, Thiamin, Vitamin D3, Vitamin B12, Vitamin B6, Manganese Sulphate, Potassium Iodide, Vitamin K1, Sodium Selenite</p>\r\n<p>Allergy Advice &ndash; For allergens, see ingredients in bold</p>\r\n<p>Milk<br />Soy</p>\r\n<p>Nutritional Information per 100ml prepared feed<br />Units (% LRV&dagger;)<br />Energy 285 kJ<br />68 kcal<br />Fat 3 g &amp;<br />of which, saturates 1.3 g<br />Carbohydrate 8.6 g<br />of which, sugars 8.5 g<br />of which, lactose 8.3 g<br />Fibre 0.6 g<br />Protein 1.4 g<br />Salt 0.04 g<br />Vitamins<br />Vitamin A 67 &micro;g RE (17%)<br />Vitamin D3 1.5 &micro;g (21%)<br />Vitamin E