(371, 'Aptamil Creamed Apricot Porridge 4-6+ Months 125g', NULL, 6, NULL, 650, NULL, 0, 'S5CVTM', 'gm', 125, 'single', 150, '1655707746.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, '<p>Making the right feeding choices for you and your baby. We&rsquo;ve been pioneering research into infant and toddler nutrition for over 50 years to help you give your baby the best start in life. We ensure only high quality grains and fruit are selected and then combine these with our unique blend of nutrients, Pronutravi+&trade;. Offering your baby a wide variety of foods along their weaning journey is important as this is when they start to form their taste preferences. Our range of unique cereals are specifically developed to introduce delicious tastes and textures as your baby progresses.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>How to use:</strong></p>\r\n<p>To Serve</p>\r\n<p>Using a clean bowl and feeding spoon. Mix 1 spoonful of cereal with. 2 1/2 spoonfuls of warm, previously boiled water and stir. If serving warm, check temperature before feeding. As your baby&rsquo;s appetite grows use a larger spoon to make a bigger serving. This is only a guide, if you want to alter the consistency, add more or less water as required. Smooth textures are best when your baby starts weaning because they&rsquo;re easy for your baby to manage.</p>\r\n<p>Storage</p>\r\n<p>Please store this product in a cool dry place (not in the fridge) and once opened use within 28 days. Packaged in a protective atmosphere.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hazards and Cautions</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />Do not leave your baby alone whilst feeding. Remember to clean your baby&rsquo;s teeth, especially before bedtime.</p>\r\n<p>While every care has been taken to ensure this information is always as accurate as possible, food products are regularly improved and nutrition content may occasionally change. As a result we recommend that you always read the label carefully before using or consuming any products.</p>\r\n<p>Nutritional Reference Va